# The rest of the NP
################################################################################

#X Grammatical (noun DEM verb)
Source: {c}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {det}
kaai hu taa
dog SPC sleep
'A dog (you do not know about) sleeps.'

#X Ungrammatical (DEM noun verb)
Source: {c}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: u
Phenomena: {det}
hu kaai taa
SPC dog sleep
'A dog (you do not know about) sleeps.'

#X Grammatical (noun verb)
Source: {c}
Vetted: {f}
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {det}
kaai taa
dog sleep
'A dog is sleeping.'
